## âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions

### 1. Prerequisites
- âœ… Salesforce Org (Developer or Sandbox)  
- âœ… Freshdesk Account with **API Key**  
- âœ… Remote Site Settings enabled in Salesforce for the Freshdesk API endpoint  

### 2. Salesforce Configuration

#### ğŸ”¹ Custom Labels
- `Helpdesk_Username` â†’ `<your API key>`  
- `Helpdesk_URL` â†’ `https://<yourdomain>.freshdesk.com/api/v2/tickets`

#### ğŸ”¹ Apex Class
- `Ps_HelpDeskTicketUtils.cls`  
  - Contains `FreshdeskTicketWrapper` class to hold ticket details.  
  - `createTickets` method handles the callout using Basic Authentication.  
  - `cc_emails` can be included as a **List<String>** if needed.

#### ğŸ”¹ Trigger / Handler (Optional)
- `CaseTriggerHandler.cls` can be used to automatically send Cases to Freshdesk.
